'''亨利·希姆斯'''（{{lang-en|'''Henry Sims'''}}，{{bd|1991年|12月4日||}}），[[美国|美国]]职业[[篮球运动员|篮球运动员]]，大学毕业并效力于[[乔治城大学|乔治城大学]]，现效力于[[NBA|NBA]]的[[布魯克林籃網|布魯克林籃網]]。

==职业生涯==
希姆斯从乔治城大学毕业后，他决定参加[[2012年NBA选秀|2012年NBA选秀]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.nba.com/news/2012-draft-early-entries/index.html |title=NBA announces early entry candidates for 2012 NBA Draft |publisher=NBA.com |date=2012-05-03 |accessdate=2014-12-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120609012927/http://www.nba.com/news/2012-draft-early-entries/index.html |archive-date=2012-06-09 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>，不过他没有被任何一支球队选中。希姆斯随后代表[[犹他爵士|犹他爵士]]队参加了同年的[[NBA夏季联赛|NBA夏季联赛]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.nba.com/bulls/news/bulls-announce-2012-summer-league-roster.html|title=Bulls announce 2012 summer league roster|publisher=NBA.com|date=2012-07-09|accessdate=2014-12-06|archive-date=2020-02-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200213020330/https://www.nba.com/bulls/news/bulls-announce-2012-summer-league-roster.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，并场均可以贡献4.3分2.3个[[篮板球|篮板球]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.nba.com/summer-league/2012/players/sl_henry_sims/|title=Henry Sims #22 Center Jazz|publisher=NBA.com|date=2012-07|accessdate=2014-12-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150210180027/http://www.nba.com/summer-league/2012/players/sl_henry_sims/|archive-date=2015-02-10|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。2012年9月10日，希姆斯被[[纽约尼克斯|纽约尼克斯]]签下<ref name="realgm">{{cite web|url=http://basketball.realgm.com/player/Henry-Sims/Summary/2371|title=Henry Sims Player Profile – RealGM|publisher=REAL GM|date=2012|accessdate=2014-12-06|archive-date=2014-12-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141207084509/http://basketball.realgm.com/player/Henry-Sims/Summary/2371|dead-url=no}}</ref>，然而，他在10月27日又被尼克斯队裁员<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.insidehoops.com/blog/?p=11312|title=Knicks waive Oscar Bellfield, John Shurna, Mychel Thompson, Henry Sims|publisher=NBA.com|date=2012-07-09|accessdate=2014-12-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131029201607/http://www.insidehoops.com/blog/?p=11312|archive-date=2013-10-29|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://voice.hupu.com/nba/1154164.html|title=尼克斯裁掉贝尔菲尔德等4球员|publisher=虎扑体育|date=2012-07-09|accessdate=2014-12-06|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304132816/http://voice.hupu.com/nba/1154164.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。同年11月，希姆斯与[[NBA发展联盟|NBA发展联盟]]的艾利湾鹰队签下一份合同<ref name="realgm" />。次年2月4日，希姆斯入选了当年的NBA发展联盟全明星阵容<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.nba.com/dleague/news/2013_nba_development_league_all_star_rosters_announced_2013_02_04.html |title=2013 NBA Development League All-Star Game Rosters Announced |publisher=NBA.COM |date=2013-02-04 |accessdate=2014-12-06 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131022065410/http://www.nba.com/dleague/news/2013_nba_development_league_all_star_rosters_announced_2013_02_04.html |archivedate=2013-10-22 }}</ref>。

2013年3月4日，希姆斯与[[新奥尔良黄蜂|新奥尔良黄蜂]]签下一份为期10天的合同<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.nba.com/hornets/news/hornets-sign-sims-10-day-contract|title=HORNETS SIGN SIMS TO 10-DAY CONTRACT|publisher=NBA.COM|date=2013-03-04|accessdate=2014-12-06|archive-date=2019-12-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191206143118/https://www.nba.com/hornets/news/hornets-sign-sims-10-day-contract|dead-url=no}}</ref>。希姆斯为黄蜂出战两场，场均贡献两分一个篮板球<ref name="realgm" />。他在8天后被球队裁员，因为球队签下了[[路易斯·阿蒙德森|路易斯·阿蒙德森]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.nba.com/hornets/news/hornets-sign-amundson-0|title=HORNETS SIGN AMUNDSON; Waive Henry Sims|publisher=NBA.COM|date=2013-03-12|accessdate=2014-12-06|archive-date=2013-03-16|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6FAAcjaBj?url=http://www.nba.com/hornets/news/hornets-sign-amundson-0|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://voice.hupu.com/nba/1351436.html|title=正式：黄蜂签下路易斯-阿蒙德森|publisher=虎扑体育|date=2013-03-13|accessdate=2014-12-06|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304200435/http://voice.hupu.com/nba/1351436.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。之后他重返坎顿剑客队，但在4月1日，他的合同被坎顿剑客买断<ref name="realgm" />。一天以后，希姆斯和[[菲律宾|菲律宾]]篮球联赛的皮特伦火箭助推器队签下一份合同<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.sportando.net/eng/world/asia/53489/henry-sims-signs-with-petron-blaze-in-the-philippines.html|title=Henry Sims signs with Petron Blaze in the Philippines|publisher=sportando|date=2013-04-02|accessdate=2014-12-06|archive-date=2013-10-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131029195202/http://www.sportando.net/eng/world/asia/53489/henry-sims-signs-with-petron-blaze-in-the-philippines.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

希姆斯代表夏洛特山猫队出战了2013年的NBA[[拉斯维加斯|拉斯维加斯]]夏季联赛<ref>{{cite web|url=http://china.nba.com/news/4/2013-07-13/1218/14290.html|title=马刺队69-68险胜山猫|publisher=nba.com (CHINA)|date=2013-07-13|accessdate=2014-12-06|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141217120406/http://china.nba.com/news/4/2013-07-13/1218/14290.html|archivedate=2014-12-17}}</ref>。同年9月30日，希姆斯接受了克利夫兰骑士队的邀请，签下一份训练营合同<ref>{{cite web|url=http://voice.hupu.com/nba/1518050.html|title=亨利-希姆斯确认参加骑士训练营|publisher=虎扑体育|date=2013-09-30|author=阿克伦灯塔报|accessdate=2014-12-06|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304201524/http://voice.hupu.com/nba/1518050.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在骑士期间，希姆斯两次被下放到NBA发展联盟的坎顿剑客队<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.nba.com/cavaliers/releases/assign-felix-sims-131205|title=Cavs Assign Sims and Felix to Charge|publisher=nba.com|date=2013-12-06|accessdate=2014-12-06|archive-date=2020-11-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201126171317/https://www.nba.com/cavaliers/releases/assign-felix-sims-131205|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.nba.com/cavaliers/releases/assign-felix-sims-karasev-131211|title=Cavs Assign Felix, Karasev and Sims to Charge|publisher=nba.com|date=2013-12-12|accessdate=2014-12-06|archive-date=2020-11-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201126203919/https://www.nba.com/cavaliers/releases/assign-felix-sims-karasev-131211|dead-url=no}}</ref>。次年2月20日，他与[[厄尔·克拉克|厄尔·克拉克]]一起被骑士队交易到[[费城76人|费城76人]]队，以换取76人队的[[中锋_(篮球)|中锋]]斯班瑟·霍伊斯<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.nba.com/sixers/news/sixers-acquire-two-second-round-picks-2014-nba-draft-cleveland-cavaliers|title=Sixers Acquire Two Second-Round Picks in 2014 NBA Draft From Cleveland Cavaliers|publisher=nba.com|date=2014-02-20|accessdate=2014-12-06|archive-date=2015-10-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151026231216/http://www.nba.com/sixers/news/sixers-acquire-two-second-round-picks-2014-nba-draft-cleveland-cavaliers|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://voice.hupu.com/nba/1630881.html|title=骑士用希姆斯+克拉克换得76人霍伊斯|publisher=nba.com|date=2014-02-20|accessdate=2014-12-06|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304185220/http://voice.hupu.com/nba/1630881.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

在2014年3月22日，希姆斯在输给[[芝加哥公牛|芝加哥公牛]]拿下刷新职业生涯新高的15个篮板球，外加18分<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.nba.com/games/20140322/PHICHI/gameinfo.html|title=Notebook: Bulls 91, 76ers 81|publisher=nba.com|date=2014-03-22|accessdate=2014-12-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141130223703/http://www.nba.com/games/20140322/PHICHI/gameinfo.html|archive-date=2014-11-30|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。13天之后，希姆斯又在面对波士顿凯尔特人的比赛中贡献24分，刷新职业生涯新高<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.nba.com/games/20140404/PHIBOS/gameinfo.html|title=Notebook: 76ers 111, Celtics 102|publisher=nba.com|date=2014-04-04|accessdate=2014-12-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150114005943/http://www.nba.com/games/20140404/PHIBOS/gameinfo.html|archive-date=2015-01-14|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://voice.hupu.com/nba/1662038.html|title=76人主帅谈胜利：我们正在交好运|publisher=虎扑体育|date=2014-04-04|accessdate=2014-12-06|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304191522/http://voice.hupu.com/nba/1662038.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

